OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FCarrie Johnson has said there could be
OL,8,F"up to 1,000, if not more" John
OL,9,FWorboys victims, as she said she had
OL,10,Fbeen contacted by people who believe
OL,11,Fthey were assaulted by the serial
OL,12,Frapist.
OL,14,FSpeaking to Good Morning Britain,
OL,15,FJohnson, the wife of former Prime
OL,16,FMinister Boris Johnson, recounted her
OL,17,Fencounter with Worboys and the journey
OL,18,Fshe went through to give evidence
OL,19,Fagainst him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
