OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FShe said: "The truth is that his
OL,8,Fcrimes span from, what we know, from
OL,9,F2000 up to when he was convicted in
OL,10,F2009.
OL,12,F"And he was a cab driver for that
OL,13,Fduration, out potentially every night
OL,14,Fin his cab, so there could be up to
OL,15,F1,000 if not more than that."
OL,17,FWorboys is serving a life sentence
OL,18,Fafter luring women into his taxi late
OL,19,Fat night, pretending he had won money
OL,20,Fand offering them celebratory drinks
OL,21,Flaced with drugs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
