OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,F'This might really help keep him
OL,8,Fbehind bars for good'
OL,10,FJohnson highlighted that tourists and
OL,11,Fforeign visitors often use black cabs,
OL,12,Fand they may never report their crimes.
OL,14,FShe said: "I think there'll be women
OL,15,Fwho, like me, were drugged, who might
OL,16,Fnot realise they were drugged, who
OL,17,Fjust thought, God, maybe that last
OL,18,Fdrink didn't sit well with me, or, or
OL,19,Fnow maybe they've seen what's happened
OL,20,Fand they think, 'Oh well, it's done'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
