OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,F"I would urge them to come forward if
OL,8,Fthey can."
OL,10,FShe said the scale of Worboys crimes
OL,11,F"could be enormous."
OL,13,FJohnson also highlighted the recent
OL,14,Fbroadcast of Believe Me, a four-part
OL,15,Fminiseries detailing Worboys' victims'
OL,16,Ffight for justice, started on ITV on
OL,17,FMay 10, as a further way awareness has
OL,18,Fbeen raised about his crimes.
OL,20,FShe said as a result of the broadcast,
OL,21,F"more women are now coming forward."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
