OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FJohnson said people had messaged her
OL,8,Fon Instagram, "telling me that they
OL,9,Fthink they are in Worboys' cab too."
OL,11,FShe said she hoped "that this might
OL,12,Freally help keep him behind bars for
OL,13,Fgood."
OL,15,FJohnson was 19 when she got in
OL,16,FWorboys' cab after a night out in
OL,17,FChelsea. He offered to take her home
OL,18,Fdespite her not having enough money.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
