OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FHe claimed he had won a lot of money
OL,8,Fat a casino and wanted to celebrate,
OL,9,Foffering Johnson alcohol.
OL,11,FPolice later said this was a method he
OL,12,Fused to drug his victims by spiking
OL,13,Falcohol, often repeating the casino
OL,14,Fstory.
OL,16,FJohnson said she drank a small amount
OL,17,Fof the alcohol offered but declined
OL,18,Fhis other propositions before Worboys
OL,19,Feventually took her home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
