OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FHe offered her his number when she got
OL,8,Fout of the taxi and she later used
OL,9,Fthis as evidence against him in court.
OL,11,FMinutes later in her house, she became
OL,12,Funwell and began vomiting.
OL,14,F'There could be up to 1,000 if not
OL,15,Fmore than that'
OL,17,FJohnson has recently called for a
OL,18,Fculture change by the police in their
OL,19,Fapproach to rape and claimed some
OL,20,Fofficers didn't take her seriously.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
