OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FShe told GMB: "If my car was stolen,
OL,8,Fif I went to the police, I think they
OL,9,Fwould believe me, and I think they
OL,10,Fwould write down the evidence
OL,11,Faccordingly.
OL,13,F"But if I go and say I've been raped,
OL,14,FI'm not sure they necessarily do. They
OL,15,Fat least don't act like they do. They
OL,16,Fquestion one's integrity."
OL,18,FLast week the Parole Board said
OL,19,FWorboys "continues to represent a high
OL,20,Frisk of committing further serious
OL,21,Fsexual offences against women".
OL,26,@{D@IOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
