OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FWorboys indicated to the board he
OL,8,Fwould not be requesting to be freed,
OL,9,Fso a scheduled public hearing was
OL,10,Fcancelled.
OL,12,FParole papers said the 68-year-old
OL,13,F"accepts that he does not currently
OL,14,Fmeet the test for release" and claims
OL,15,Fto feel "enormous regret, remorse and
OL,16,Fshame".
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@ZO]wD@IOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
