OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FWhen asked about Worboys' reported
OL,8,Fremorse, Johnson said: "I don't
OL,9,Fbelieve it. No, I don't believe in the
OL,10,Flast couple of years that he has had a
OL,11,Fpersonality transplant."
OL,13,FWorboys was first jailed in 2009 for
OL,14,F19 sexual offences linked to attacks
OL,15,Fon 12 victims between October 2006 and
OL,16,FFebruary 2008 in London, and was given
OL,17,Fan indefinite sentence for public
OL,18,Fprotection with a minimum term of
OL,19,Feight years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
