CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FIn December 2017, a Parole Board panel
OL,8,Fdecided he was ready for release,
OL,9,Fsparking a legal challenge by two of
OL,10,Fhis victims that successfully got the
OL,11,Fdecision overturned.
OL,13,FAmid outrage over the battle, rules
OL,14,Fwere then changed to allow some parole
OL,15,Fhearings to be held in public and
OL,16,Fpermit better scrutiny of the
OL,17,Fprocesses used.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
