CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1779300667
OL,3,CCarrie Johnson says there could be
OL,4,C'1,000, if not more' victims of John
OL,5,CWorboys
OL,7,FThe publicity around the case led
OL,8,Ffurther victims to come forward, and
OL,9,FWorboys was charged with more crimes
OL,10,Fdating between 2000 and 2008, which he
OL,11,Fadmitted.
OL,13,FIn 2019, he was handed two life
OL,14,Fsentences with a minimum term of six
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,17,FWorboys will be considered for parole
OL,18,Fagain in around two years' time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
